Schipper Translate Privacy Policy
07/12/2025
This extension collects user data in the following ways:

1. user clicks
2. mouse position
3. website content -- specifically text

This user data is used only for purposes necessary to the extension. These uses are:

1. Tracking user clicks to select translation mode
2. Tracking user clicks on the translate text button to translate in-extension
3. Tracking user clicks to translate highlighted text
4. Tracking user clicks to revert translated text or to remove tooltip
5. Mouse position is used to determine where the tooltip will show up on the screen
6. Text on websites is copied and used in the translation, which is then returned to the screen

This user data is not shared with any other parties
